{"tid":2337220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博抗疫榜 港跌至13","createTime":"2020-12-23T06:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T07:38:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f8333fac2684a1ec87a0757026a127ea7b38ad1","tid":2337220,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/VCLU4G3DZNG6HGOZRXZWEAVO3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FVCLU4G3DZNG6HGOZRXZWEAVO3I%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=b5c5461c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201223%2FVCLU4G3DZNG6HGOZRXZWEAVO3I%2F&h=bbb60e9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201223/VCLU4G3DZNG6HGOZRXZWEAVO3I/</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博抗疫榜 港跌至13<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PMohKtJZ9AIvvJ5M_xOBkwoEfNQ=/4464x2184/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LENYVB22RBBNFKEBRVZU5NS5ZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPMohKtJZ9AIvvJ5M_xOBkwoEfNQ%3D%2F4464x2184%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLENYVB22RBBNFKEBRVZU5NS5ZU.jpg&h=e673818b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港在彭博抗疫排行榜下跌一位排第13名。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎繼續全球肆虐，彭博（Bloomberg）公佈最新「抗疫韌性排行榜」（The Covid Resilience Ranking），列出全球武漢肺炎疫情下最安全和最不安全的國家或地區，香港下跌一位至第13位，中國大陸排行第9位，首3位分別是新西蘭、台灣及澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭續稱冠 中國第九<br />\n<br />\n彭博上月首度公佈抗疫韌性排名，分析全球53個經濟體控制疫情的成效，排名昨日更新。香港下跌一位排名第13；新西蘭繼續排名首位，台灣上升一位至第二位，第三至第五依序是澳洲、挪威、新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n彭博排行榜採用多項指標，本港最近一個月每10萬人新增。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n彭博"},{"pid":"d67a37d6fdf259fc2cf36bfca266bb813c213941","tid":2337220,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:38:31.000Z","msg":"台灣輸俾紐西蘭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}